import React from "react";
import {
  Box,
  Heading,
  Link,
  Image,
  Text,
  Divider,
  HStack,
  Tag,
  Wrap,
  WrapItem,
  SpaceProps,
  useColorModeValue,
  Container,
  VStack,
  Input,
  Button,
  Center,
} from "@chakra-ui/react";
const Blog = () => {
  return (
    <Container maxW={"7xl"} p="12">
      <Heading as="h1" fontWeight="bold" textAlign="center" fontSize="80px">
        BLOG & ARTICLE
      </Heading>
      <Text textAlign="center">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Illum
        reiciendis perferendis,?
      </Text>
      <Center>
      <Box alignContent="center" display="flex">
      <Input
      ml ="150px"
      mt="30px"
      textAlign="center"
      w="500px"
        placeholder="search  articles, news and recipes"
      ></Input>
      <Button bg="black" color="white" mt='30px' >Search</Button>
      </Box>
      </Center>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default Blog;
